<D>__{it's not important. i just had one last year.}
<C>__{ned}
<D>__{well, i'm taking you out to celebrate!}
<A>__{in the b.g. the slimy defendant pulls a gun and forces citizens... including judge arugula... up against the wall, robbing them!}
