<D>__{you're so sweet. you don't have to. you gave me a present last year. those lovely ginzu knives.}
<C>__{ned}
<D>__{yeah... aren't they great! they last forever. and you can cut right through a shoe with 'em!}
<A>__{as they walk off, we hold on a close shot of a newspaper. the headline reads: ex con stalks cop lawyer ned ravine! below it is a picture of max shady, eyes wide with psychotic rage... a huge cigar in his mouth, wearing a garish hawaiian shirt. hands lower the newspaper... revealing max himself, with the same cigar, shirt and crazed look on his face.}
